"msg":"排球既技術"},{"pid":"67be2e9e8f2a535800e678b10da9a4480ded822e","tid":2126423,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"佢條撚樣得啖笑<br />\n阻住其他人上位"},{"pid":"3df0d0479bb403e2d16f6ace0785f88f6a09ba8a","tid":2126423,"uid":199081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"大家有無踢過11人比賽? 有無聽過&rdquo;豆&ldquo;住中場<br />\n我就同過一個中場中踼過, 一樣無身形無高度, 佢唔係好扭得, 又唔係最快<br />\n但基本功好札扎實, 控波, 包位, 長短傳, 入波, 樣樣有, 而佢可以係成場零失誤, 你唔洗幫佢, 但佢會衝過黎幫你<br />\n我自問都踢過好多比賽, 但如果對手強, 難免會怯場緊張<br />\n但有佢在場, 你會好放心, 可以發揮返自己水準, 自然成隊波生哂"},{"pid":"e2aa6bcd530d402305057cafe5102f452c9c8287","tid":2126423,"uid":84081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"1. 商業價值 IG多followers<br />\n2. 髮型代言人<br />\n3. BLM<br />\n4. 腦震盪代言人<br />\n5. 記者採訪對象 同巴洛迪利一樣唔踢多新聞過踢"},{"pid":"3472ef526c62672b10660ce3acb1c5fd0e39c348","tid":2126423,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"全能"},{"pid":"ca1feee0ba3936f9083b182a0542072d42b8e972","tid":2126423,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"BLM"},{"pid":"146920ed9c81de4f07ed465c3827ee53cf0a1e51","tid":2126423,"uid":53959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"359b4622a0ff537806d37d3bdeb1ae9eab457885","tid":2126423,"uid":159821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"逗住型中場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"要人逗住既逗住型中場"},{"pid":"ffe1f888438042792b683d7c79730a6efa4cb9f6","tid":2126423,"uid":298780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"成日都推甩腳<br />\n波都護唔好<br />\n比d直線都仲可以<br />\nD短傳真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"0569523c93c8f02354bbd65cd6ef1b7e9edfe9dc","tid":2126423,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"夠潮，做Icon"},{"pid":"a76222cbd10039b5963d764ec40272b